ue of the stock.=09But eventually =E2=80=94=C2=A0like, three years ago? =E2=
=80=94=C2=A0people realized that there was a flaw in that reasoning. While =
the value of a company=E2=80=99s cash flows probably=C2=A0does=C2=A0set a r=
