<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Basically the story of the complaint=C2=A0is t=
hat four guys =E2=80=9Cattended Pepperdine and played on the school=E2=80=
=99s baseball team together=E2=80=9D in the mid-2010s. After graduation, on=
e of them ended up working =E2=80=9Con finance-related matters=E2=80=9D at =
Jack in the Box Inc.; the other three played minor-league baseball. The Jac=
k-in-the-Box guy hung out with his former teammates and allegedly discussed=
 his company=E2=80=99s planned acquisition of Del Taco Restaurants Inc. in =
front of them, including on a four-hour Zoom call about the deal while in a=
 car with one of the minor leaguers.<a class=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#fo=
otnote-3" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border=
-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: none=
 !important; background-color: transparent !important; display: inline-bloc=
k;">
<span>[3]</span>
</a>=C2=A0The minor leaguers then allegedly traded call options on Del Taco=
, which is bad.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The=C2=A0<em>Third=C2=A0</em>Law of Insider Tr=
ading is =E2=80=9Cdon=E2=80=99t text or email about it,=E2=80=9D and these =
guys allegedly did. But they actually did a nice job of sending <em>good </=
em>texts:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">In their initial texts, Qsar, Witherspoon, and=
 Individual 1 demonstrated that they knew they had obtained material nonpub=
lic information by attempting to concoct an alternative explanation for the=
ir eventual trades.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">For example, on or about October 5, 2021, With=
erspoon texted Qsar and Individual 1, =E2=80=9C[c]heck out this stock guys =
Del taco, this chart is looking bullish to me. Might try to gamble on some =
options or something, I love to eat at del taco.=E2=80=9D =E2=80=A6</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Qsar responded, =E2=80=9CI=E2=80=99m thinking =
about it too[.] Chart looks primed to boom[.] What=E2=80=99s it [sic] 52 we=
ek high?=E2=80=9D</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Witherspoon responded, =E2=80=9C$11.99[.] Coul=
d see it hitting $10 easy[.]=E2=80=9D</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Qsar responded, =E2=80=9CIf we break 10 new 52=
 week highs could follow[.] The payout could be ridiculous if we buy the Ja=
nuary 2022 calls[.]=E2=80=9D</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I dunno. If you assume they were insider tradi=
ng, then I suppose those texts =E2=80=9Cdemonstrated that they knew they ha=
d obtained material nonpublic information by attempting to concoct an alter=
native explanation for their eventual trades.=E2=80=9D But if you=C2=A0<em>=
don=E2=80=99t=C2=A0</em>assume that, then I suppose it is nice to have text=
s saying =E2=80=9CI like the stock=E2=80=9D before you go out and buy call =
options.</p>
