<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The rough rule of US insider trading law is th=
at it is illegal to trade stock when (1) you have material nonpublic inform=
ation and (2) you have some obligation to somebody not to use it to trade t=
hat stock. Most straightforwardly:</p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: disc; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;">=
=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">A company has fiduciary obligations to=
 its shareholders, and isn=E2=80=99t supposed to trade in its own stock wit=
hout disclosing all material information.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom=
: 5px;">A company=E2=80=99s employees have fiduciary obligations to the com=
pany, and aren=E2=80=99t supposed to trade its stock when they have materia=
l nonpublic information.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">A company=
=E2=80=99s various service providers =E2=80=94=C2=A0bankers, lawyers, etc. =
=E2=80=94=C2=A0have confidentiality obligations to the company and aren=E2=
=80=99t supposed to use inside information to trade its stock.</li>
</ul>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">There are more complicated cases:</p>
<ul style=3D"list-style-type: disc; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;">=
=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">The employees (and bankers, lawyers, e=
tc.) of the=C2=A0<em>acquirer </em>in a possible merger have obligations to=
 that acquirer, and are not supposed to use inside information to trade the=
=C2=A0<em>target=E2=80=99s=C2=A0</em>stock.</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bott=
om: 5px;">A <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/348873=
93.257355/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtM=
DctMDMvaW5zaWRlci10cmFkaW5nLWlzLWJldHRlci1mcm9tLWhvbWU_Y21waWQ9QkJEMDQwMTI0=
X01PTkVZU1RVRkYmdXRtX21lZGl1bT1lbWFpbCZ1dG1fc291cmNlPW5ld3NsZXR0ZXImdXRtX3R=
lcm09MjQwNDAxJnV0bV9jYW1wYWlnbj1tb25leXN0dWZm/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB6ad8=
ff32" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" styl=
e=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width:=
 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-=
color: #ccc;">romantic partner</a>=C2=A0or <a href=3D"https://link.mail.blo=
ombergbusiness.com/click/34887393.257355/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS=
92aWV3L2FydGljbGVzLzIwMTQtMDgtMTgvb25lLWdvbGYtY291cnNlLXRoYXQtcy1ncmVhdC1mb=
