mscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !i=
mportant; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bo=
ttom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  talked</a> a few <a href=3D"h=
ttps://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/34887393.257355/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3=
cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDctMDMvaW5zaWRlci10cmFka=
W5nLWlzLWJldHRlci1mcm9tLWhvbWU_Y21waWQ9QkJEMDQwMTI0X01PTkVZU1RVRkYmdXRtX21l=
ZGl1bT1lbWFpbCZ1dG1fc291cmNlPW5ld3NsZXR0ZXImdXRtX3Rlcm09MjQwNDAxJnV0bV9jYW1=
